org.gwtbootstrap3.client.ui.form.validator
Interface ValidationMessages

All Superinterfaces:
com.google.gwt.i18n.client.Constants, com.google.gwt.i18n.client.ConstantsWithLookup, com.google.gwt.i18n.shared.Localizable, com.google.gwt.i18n.client.LocalizableResource
public interface ValidationMessages
extends com.google.gwt.i18n.client.ConstantsWithLookup

Validation messages. Message functions should be the key with "_" replacing any periods. This allows the ValidationMessageResolver to find the message by key.

Author:
Steven Jardine
